Kh8 22. Nxd5 $18) 21. Rxf3 Qxf3+ 22. Qg2 $16 Rxf5 $140 23. Bxf5 Qxf5 24. Qxa8+
$18) 19. Kh1 Qh5 20. Bxe5 ({Obviously now} 20. gxf3 $4 {cannot be played, as
